  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level 13 is a spot-the-difference horror maze inspired by the Backrooms and games like P.T., The Exit 8, and I'm On Observation Duty.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ anomalies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 - 3 hours playtime</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully navigate  this unsettling apartment stairwell and descend each floor in search of the exit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/ac193294a4d6d181f0696a60b0bd8aec.poster.avif?t=1741260617\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/ac193294a4d6d181f0696a60b0bd8aec.webm?t=1741260617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter anything unusual (missing objects, moving objects, n̷͇͗e̷̳͆i̵̹͘ġ̴̫h̴̨̏ḃ̴̼ȯ̴̬r̶̖͗s̸͚̃, etc.)  return upstairs to find reality again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/8edc54d0dbae0e81a9d4e089754ecb22.poster.avif?t=1741260617\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/8edc54d0dbae0e81a9d4e089754ecb22.webm?t=1741260617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level 13 is a spot-the-difference horror maze inspired by the Backrooms and games like P.T., The Exit 8, and I'm On Observation Duty.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ anomalies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 - 3 hours playtime</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully navigate  this unsettling apartment stairwell and descend each floor in search of the exit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/ac193294a4d6d181f0696a60b0bd8aec.poster.avif?t=1741260617\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/ac193294a4d6d181f0696a60b0bd8aec.webm?t=1741260617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter anything unusual (missing objects, moving objects, n̷͇͗e̷̳͆i̵̹͘ġ̴̫h̴̨̏ḃ̴̼ȯ̴̬r̶̖͗s̸͚̃, etc.)  return upstairs to find reality again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/8edc54d0dbae0e81a9d4e089754ecb22.poster.avif?t=1741260617\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469600/extras/8edc54d0dbae0e81a9d4e089754ecb22.webm?t=1741260617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
